  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You touch a dying creature, healing them just enough to prevent them from dying from their wounds.</em></p><p><strong>Healing Spell</strong></p><p>This spell has no effect on &amp;reference[construct]{constructs}.</p><ul><li><p>If the target was at 0 hit points but still alive, they become stable and no longer need to roll death saving throws. This effect ends if the target takes any damage. If the target takes no damage, is stable for 10 minutes, and still has 0 hit points, they regain 1 hit point.</p></li></ul>",
      "chat": "<p><span style=\"font-family:'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track)\">Healing Spell</strong></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(207, 210, 218);font-family:'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(37, 40, 48);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif\">This spell has no effect on constructs.</span></p><ul style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);margin:0.5em 0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 1.5em;color:rgb(207, 210, 218);font-family:'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(37, 40, 48);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\"><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track)\"><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);margin:0.5em 0px\"><span style=\"font-family:'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif\">If the target was at 0 hit points but still alive, they become stable and no longer need to roll death saving throws. This effect ends if the target takes any damage. If the target takes no damage, is stable for 10 minutes, and still has 0 hit points, they regain 1 hit point.</span></p></li></ul>"
